snippet.textDisplay:
I have dissected the lyrics and you will realise the actual magic behind lyrics of this song....its a whole conversation between two people.



Duniya Ton Akk Gaye Aa
Tere Nal Lag Gaye Aa
Duniya Ton Akk Gaye Aa
Tere Nal Lag Gaye Aa

Har Velle Rehnda Channa
Tera Hi Khayal Ve

Teriyan Adawan
Teri Ankhiyan Ne Maareya
Teriyan Adawan
Teri Ankhiyan Ne Maareya

Saanu Chann Maahiya Teri
Thagyan Ne Maariya


First Part :  {the first part shows how men are more forward in expressing their love and desire to be with the woman of their life} The guy is expressing his love for the girl. He praises her eyes, her beauty and her impact. He tells that i keep thinking about you. I have left this world and i am just connected to you.




Lambi raat juddiyan di
Sannu channu tu chaiye da 
Ni lor kamaiyaan di

Second part: {Here the girl and boy are separated and now they have distance between them...the guy is gone because the girl never reciprocated his love)



Ik Waari Jawe Fer
Mudke Tu Aauna Nai
Saaḍe Wal Maahiya Fer
Phera Tu Te Paunda Nai

Lokan Kol Bahna Ae Tu
Door Sathon Rahna Ae Tu

Kahnde Loki Laake Tu
Toṛ Nibhaunda Nai
Tere Baare Khabran Ae
Pakkiyaan Ne Maareya

Saanu Chann Maahiya Teri
Thagyan Ne Maariya


3rd Part: {The girl starts missing the guy and now though she is shy and doesnt openly say that she loves him too but due to shyness she only complains about him that} Why dont you come back once you are gone, Once you are gone you never bother to meet me again(like you are kind of careless in your ways) and Unfortunately i have heard news about you from other people that you are not trustworthy 




Ankhiyan Ch Haan Teri
Bulliyan Te Naa Ve
Ikko Waari Dil Naal
Kar Lai Salaah Ve

Dil Utte Maahiya
Kithe Zor Koyi Chalda
Sanu Te Bharosa Nahio
Tera Ik Pal Da

Gallaan Teriyaan Jhooṭhiyan
Te Sacchiyan Ne Maareya


Last part : Now the girl and guy are infront of each other but they both have some sweet and playful complaints against each other....the guy says that though your lips always refrain from admitting your love for me your eyes speak the opposite...why dont you confess your feelings once and for all...but the girl being shy again refrains from openly admitting her secret likeness for the guy by saying that i dont have control over my heart and i dont trust you (because you left me once before so why should i admit my love for you).
